---
---
<section class="broker">
  <div class="broker__intro">
    <h2 class="broker__heading">Your Advocate. Your Advisor. Your Resource — For Free.</h2>
    <p class="broker__subtext">
      Working with a broker <strong>costs you nothing</strong> and gives you everything: unbiased
      guidance, personal service, and someone in your corner every step of the way.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="founder">
    <img
      src="/images/founder.jpg"
      alt="Matthew Garza, founder of Superior Senior Benefits"
      class="founder__photo"
      width="447"
      height="447"
    />
    <div class="founder__bio">
      <h3 class="founder__name">Meet Our Founder</h3>
      <p class="founder__text">
        With over 7+ years of industry experience, Matthew Garza has helped countless seniors get
        covered by Medicare. Having managed over 400+ active clients at once in the past and
        representing over 25 carriers, Matthew brings unmatched expertise and dedication to every
        client relationship.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="broker__cards">
    <div class="broker-card">
      <img src="/images/no-extra-fees-icon.png" alt="No extra fees illustration" class="broker-card__icon" />
      <div>
        <p class="broker-card__title">No Extra Fees.</p>
        <p class="broker-card__text">
          The Premium you pay is the same whether you go through a broker or directly to the carrier.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="broker-card">
      <img src="/images/human-guidance-icon.png" alt="Human guidance illustration" class="broker-card__icon" />
      <div>
        <p class="broker-card__title">Authentic Human Guidance.</p>
        <p class="broker-card__text">
          When you go direct, you get only one option, long hold times, and buggy automated phone
          systems. When you work with us, you get a real human expert.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .broker {
    padding: 4rem var(--page-padding);
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Intro ── */
  .broker__intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .broker__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .broker__subtext {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.25vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 90ch;
  }

  /* ── Founder card ── */
  .founder {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    background-color: var(--color-card-tan);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .founder__photo {
    width: clamp(180px, 18vw, 360px);
    height: clamp(180px, 18vw, 360px);
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .founder__name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.1vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .founder__text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.15vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── Two cards ── */
  .broker__cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .broker-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
    background-color: var(--color-card-tan);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .broker-card__icon {
    width: clamp(72px, 8vw, 150px);
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .broker-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.25vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .broker-card__text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.1vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .founder {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .founder__photo {
      width: 100%;
      height: 320px;
    }

    .broker__cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .broker {
      padding: 3rem var(--page-padding);
    }

    .broker__intro {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .founder {
      padding: 1.25rem;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .founder__photo {
      height: 240px;
    }

    .broker-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .broker-card__icon {
      width: 90px;
    }
  }
</style>
